As a user, I want to be able to connect Money Trackr to my Facebook, so that I can inform my friends using facebook.

As a user, I want to be able to create a new friend tab, so that the related information and amount of money owed can be specified.

As a user, I want to be able to know all the past history, so that I can keep track of my money flow from time to time.

As a user, I want to be able to create a new friend tab under the same friend twice, so that old amount and new amount of money will be added up.

As a user, I want to be able to pay a tab, so that the amount of money owed will be deducted.

As a user, I want to be able to specify the payment method, so that I can pay it by credit card/debit card, paypal or cash.

As a user, I want to be able to create a new friend tab and specify "friend owes me" or "I owe friends", so that I can know who is the borrower and lender.

As a user, I want to be able to specify the amount of money owed when I create a new tab, so that I can know the amount of money lended/borrowed.

As a user, I want to be able to specify the details when I create a new friend tab, so that I can know the reason behind the money flow.

As a user, I want to be able to specify the borrowed date, so that I can do a better financial management.

As a user, I want to be able to specify the deadline, so that I can notice my friends about it.

As a user, I want to be able to receive notification after something is updated, so that I always know all the updated news.

